ou sont les blueberry d'antan ? blueberry a pris de la bouteille . il n'est plus aussi percutant que dans ses premiers albums . le scenario est un peu confus et les nombreux flashbacks empechent le lecteur de participer pleinement a l'aventure . le graphisme reste fidele a la tradition blueberry , mais devient parfois beaucoup trop caricatural . ||| or are the blueberry of yesteryear ? blueberry took the bottle . it is also more powerful than his first album . the scenario is somewhat confusing and many flashbacks prevent the reader to participate fully in the adventure . the design remains faithful to the tradition blueberry , but sometimes becomes too much a caricature .